Wes Montgomery - Full House - Recorded 'Live' at Tsubo
Year: 1962 (Riverside)
Label: OJC (1996)
Total time: 63:22
Bitrate: 320 kbps

This live set is notable for teaming guitarist Wes Montgomery and the Wynton Kelly Trio (comprised of pianist Kelly, bassist Paul Chambers, and drummer Jimmy Cobb) with the fiery tenor of Johnny Griffin.  As with the OJC release, six selections ( highlighted by " Blue 'n' Boogie " and Montgomery's " S.O.S." ) are augmented by " Born to Be Blue " and a pair of alternate takes. ~ Scott Yanow, AMG

Personnel:
Wes Montgomery (Guitar) 
Johnny Griffin (Tenor Saxophone) 
Wynton Kelly (Piano) 
Paul Chambers (Double Bass) 
Jimmy Cobb (Drums)
